{"tid":1927790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國總統特朗普敦促民眾不要囤積食品和日用品","createTime":"2020-03-16T04:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:14:38.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6fce334c3e22000d7f74030f7283340ac6f6ff0e","tid":1927790,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普15日敦促民眾不要囤積食品和日用品等。<br />\n<br />\n他說各大超市正在盡力滿足民眾需求，人們沒必要囤貨；他說這些超市負責人承諾會繼續開門營業，目前這些商店進貨的水平甚至超過聖誕季節。最近許多美國民眾擔心新冠病毒蔓延，大量囤積食品及衛生紙等生活用品。<br />\n<br />\n來源：美國之音中文網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107258270725742/posts/194225215362380/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107258270725742%2Fposts%2F194225215362380%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BviEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=86e4e484\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107258270725742/posts/194225215362380/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ce54d717656a182b556dbebeab7a5e28f1daec06","tid":1927790,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"傻鳩總統"},{"pid":"6a29dabdfc75c95d271270557c2cf99e79198703","tid":1927790,"uid":226466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"咁講完 咪仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8077a54ac3b7dce16c10210f895715294e623cef","tid":1927790,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"有政府，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52c3895d59e7e94713d968370dd8f31198b34d7","tid":1927790,"uid":44171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"即刻去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b7cd2ae3e4b08c3f70991e65db529074c7f5a6","tid":1927790,"uid":36134,"like":2,"dislike":3,"